{"tid":1470262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請冷處理813機場事件","createTime":"2019-08-14T04:42:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T05:28:29.000Z","uid":41045,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a025fb69245b66cb07087c5c9d07e62ce2020f33","tid":1470262,"uid":41045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:42:06.000Z","msg":"係謠言滿天飛既而家，琴晚單野最好既處理方法就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冷處理</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個仆街政府最鐘意就係要你認低威，然後佢就可以食住個勢將大家一鋪清袋，為所欲為！<br />\n<br />\n所以我地要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以靜制動</span></span>，係完結運動之後先再諗修復手法！<br />\n<br />\n最緊要最緊要一點，有法庭禁制令下我地<span style=\"color: red;\">仍然可以係機場集會</span>，請大家聚焦返繼續既抗爭！<br />\n<br />\n忘記背後，努力面前，向著公義既標桿直跑！ ！ ！"},{"pid":"c966c59ab078013cef5c98bef8e85d85eb727b28","tid":1470262,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:42:16.000Z","msg":"[基督徒入] 求求你地入機場Sing Hallelujah<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469121\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469121</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8daec500ad4601187d5c3894538171c6c621c13e","tid":1470262,"uid":41045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:42:34.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"ee5b24cc3c1532ebc8bbbdb10d0a2df6b5993c79","tid":1470262,"uid":41045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:43:10.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"c94e3abadf8d58b811f46f27ca4172c0b68a2a3d","tid":1470262,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:43:27.000Z","msg":"【重要通知】抗爭不割蓆手冊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470153</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請參閱"},{"pid":"697da0f656e5c5586bda8756930d7a618d53124a","tid":1470262,"uid":41045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:44:03.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"81e82bdda0270866b4f05cf7cf863